Date: Wed 5 May 1999
From: ProMED-mail <promed@usa.healthnet.org>

Further to post (03) referenced above, mentioning the importance
to targeted treatment -- and, we might add, prevention -- of knowing
the species of _Borrelia_ involved, we understand that the
definitive identification has been made. We would be grateful for
information on this from an authoritative source.
